data.text:
My Hometown

Owatonna, MN

How I Came to BlueSky

I came to BlueSky through a current staff connection. They had posted to the career positions and I saw it as a great opportunity to enrich my teaching experience.

My Passions as an Educator

I am a compassionate and data driven Middle School teacher with over 15 years of experience incorporating technology into the classroom. I enjoy teaching mathematics and bringing real world connections to all content areas.

My Passions and Hobbies

Outside of the classroom I enjoy coaching gymnastics, watching my children play sports, and spending time with family. In the summer I like to spend time relaxing by the water, while in the winter, most weekends are spent in gymnasiums watching gymnastics and wrestling.
